TM TT LUN VN THC S
ti: Nghin cu cc c ch u tin khc nhau lp lch thng ip
trong cc h thng iu khin qua mng CAN.
Tc gi lun vn: L Xun Tng Kho: 2012B
Ngi hng dn: Hng dn chnh: TS. Nguyn Vit Nguyn
Hng dn ph: PGS.TS. Nguyn Vn Khang
NI DUNG TM TT
1. L do chn ti
Lun vn Nghin cu cc c ch u tin khc nhau lp lch thng ip
trong cc h thng iu khin qua mng CAN cp n vn nghin cu
cc u, nhc im ca cc c ch u tin trong vic lp lch thng ip, u
im ca mng CAN so vi cc mng khc trong cc h thng thng tin cng
nghip, ch to t... V vic kt hp s dng cc c ch u tin lp lch
thng ip trong cc h thng iu khin qua mng CAN, t c hiu
qu v chnh xc cao.
2. Mc ch nghin cu ca lun vn, i tng, phm vi nghin cu
2.1 Mc ch nghin cu ca lun vn
Nghin cu l thuyt H iu khin thi gian thc, H thng iu khin
qua mng, Mng CAN v vic dng cc c ch u tin khc nhau lp lch
trong mng CAN.
2.2 i tng v phm vi nghin cu
L thuyt H iu khin thi gian thc, H thng iu khin qua mng,
Mng CAN v vic dng cc c ch u tin khc nhau lp lch trong mng
CAN.
3. Ni dung chnh ca lun vn v ng gp ca tc gi
Chng I gii thiu tng quan v v cc vn c bn h thng iu khin
qua mng NCSs.
2
Chng II l cc vn v thi gian thc, s cn thit ca lp lch thng
ip cng nh nhng u im ni bt ca mng CAN.
Chng III nghin cu v cc c ch u tin trong lp lch thng ip, u
nhc im ca chng khi ng dng trong mng CAN, cng nh xut mt
c ch u tin nhm nng cao cht lng dch v v cht lng iu khin
ca h thng.
Chng IV m phng c ch u tin tnh v u tin lai trn mt h thng,
s khc bit cng nh u im ca u tin lai so vi u tin tnh.
4. Kt lun
Cc kt qu nghin cu a ti cc kt lun sau:
1. H thng iu khin qua mng NCSs c nhng u th hn so vi cc h
thng iu khin truyn thng, mc d vn tn ti nhiu hn ch nh tr
truyn thng, nhiu tc ng nh hng ln ti cht lng iu khin.
2. Mng CAN c nhiu u im hn so vi mt s mng khc nh Round
Robin, Token Passing
3. Nhng hn ch ca cc c ch u tin tnh v ng, v vic kt hp
chng a ra mt c ch u tin lai gii quyt c nhng hn ch
trn v t c nhng ci thin sau:
- Cht lng iu khin c nng cao. Ch s ITSE cn bng hn
so vi trng hp s dng u tin tnh.
- Cht lng dch v c nng cao. Tr truyn thng qua mng
ca cc ng dng cn bng hn so vi trng hp s dng u tin tnh.
